[SN]TITLE[SN]
Man taken to hospital after flat fire in Aberdeen

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
A man has been taken to hospital following a fire at a flat in Aberdeen.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
Fire crews were called to the blaze in a second-floor property on George Street at about 05:15.
The man's condition is not thought to be serious.
